    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>onion wedges</strong> to one side of a baking tray lined with<strong> tin foil </strong>with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 10 min or until the onion is beginning to soften</p><p>While the onion is in the oven, cut your <strong>green chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646747447272-x200.jpg",
