    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat and add the <strong>brioche halves</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 2 min or until toasted and charred</p><p>Set aside until serving, reserving the pan</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>,<strong> </strong>then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
